SUMMARY:GTApreneurs March 11-2026 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Event Toronto
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\n\\*\\*You need to register on our website to attend this event and get the zoom link. RSVPing on Meetup does not mean that you are registered\, even though Meetup.com will send you an email saying that you have. Thank you. Please go here: https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-events-toronto\n\n\\*Please note this event is advertised on multiple platforms\, and we expect around 20-25 guests.\n\nDo you want more clients? Join us for GTApreneurs March 11-2026 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Event to connect with other amazing entrepreneurs\, learn something new and promote your business!\n\nThis event will feature Guest Speaker **Allan Pollett**\, SEO Guru & CEO\, Global Net Trade. Since 1998\, Allan has been working as a SEO and web marketing specialist. He is known as the "SEO Guru" having written several books on reputation management\, social media and SEO related topics. Over the years\, he has helped over a 1000 businesses get to the top of the organic search results. One of his most recent achievements is helping one of his clients generate enough revenue from their YouTube channel to buy a Lamborghini.\n\nLearn more about **Allan** here: www.AllanPollett.com\n\n**WARM-UP ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00-12:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Guest Speaker Presentation: Allan Pollett\, ***"Get found = Get more clients: Is it better to rank well in AI or in a Google search?"***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\nFree\n\n**PREMIUM EVENT ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00-12:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Guest Speaker Presentation: Allan Pollett\, ***"Get found = Get more clients: Is it better to rank well in AI or in a Google search?"***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\n* **1:00-2:00pm:** Breakout rooms (Network 1-1 with other guests)\n\n**TICKETS**\n**GTApreneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n**Non-members:** $10\n\\*Premium ticket includes Guest Contact sheet emailed to you after the event. Note: You must attend the event to receive the guest contact sheet.\n\n**Event Organizer & Host:**\n**Tammy Defoe\,** President and Business Coach\, GTApreneurs\nVisit https://gtapreneurs.com/about and https://gtapreneurs.com/business-coaching-toronto for more information about Tammy and her Business Coaching and Consulting services.\n\n**QUESTIONS ABOUT THE EVENT?**\nContact Tammy at (416) 522-7770 or info@gtapreneurs.com or book a video consultation with her here: https://tammydefoe-gtapreneurs19.zohobookings.ca/#/1
